  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "6ca78529",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 1. Carga de librerías.\n",
    "Aquí incorporaremos las librerías necesarias."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "84374a4a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Manejo de datos\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "# Dataset de ejemplo y utilidades de sklearn\n",
    "from sklearn.datasets import load_iris\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeClassifier, plot_tree\n",
    "\n",
    "# Métricas de evaluación\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, classification_report, confusion_matrix, ConfusionMatrixDisplay\n",
    "\n",
    "# Visualización\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4e888704",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2. Carga del dataset\n",
    "Usaremos el dataset del Iris, este dataset es muy usado en la comunidad de machine learning..."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
