   "source": [
    "### 5. Evaluación del algoritmo\n",
    "\n",
    "Evaluamos el desempeño del modelo sobre el conjunto de prueba usando:\n",
    "- **Accuracy** (exactitud)\n",
    "- **Reporte de clasificación** (precisión, recall, f1-score)\n",
    "- **Matriz de confusión**\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "90f6b202",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Exactitud (Accuracy): 96.67%\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "y_pred = modelo.predict(X_test)\n",
    "\n",
    "exactitud = accuracy_score(y_test, y_pred)\n",
    "print(f\"Exactitud (Accuracy): {exactitud:.2%}\") ##Muliplica x100 y anade con 2 decimales\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "08bf0a94",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Reporte de clasificación:\n",
      "\n",
      "              precision    recall  f1-score   support\n",
      "\n",
      "      setosa       1.00      1.00      1.00        10\n",
      "  versicolor       1.00      0.90      0.95        10\n",
      "   virginica       0.91      1.00      0.95        10\n",
      "\n",
      "    accuracy                           0.97        30\n",
      "   macro avg       0.97      0.97      0.97        30\n",
      "weighted avg       0.97      0.97      0.97        30\n",
      "\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "print(\"Reporte de clasificación:\\n\")\n",
    "print(classification_report(y_test, y_pred))"
   ]
  },
